item.title: Papuan add a quote by Ernesto "Che" Guevara
item.description: "At the risk of seeming ridiculous, let me say that the true revolutionary is guided by a great feeling of love. It is impossible to think of a genuine revolutionary lacking this quality." -- Ernesto "Che" Guevara

item.title: Papuan add a quote by Ernesto Che Guevara
item.description: "There are no boundaries in this struggle to the death. We cannot be indifferent to what happens anywhere in the world, for a victory by any country over imperialism is our victory; just as any country's defeat is a defeat for all of us." -- Ernesto Che Guevara
